author: Source: Las Vegas Review Journal
title: Taylor Swift supports backup dancer's nephew with $50K donation - Las Vegas Review Journal
text:
Toshi Davidson was a backup dancer for Taylor Swift's 1989 tour, but the superstar recently showed that she was the one who had his back. The singer donated $50,000 for treatment for Davidson's 13-month-old nephew, Ayden, who was diagnosed with cancer.
